Minosiro is a collection of resources.

1. Overview

Minoshiro integrates three steps of archiving:
- Saving data in various formats.
- Maintaining the storage to speed up access.
- Handy web interface for lookups.

2. Structure of The Source Code

# 2.1. Main directory of minosiro's source code.
minosiro/
# 2.2. The library that supports minosiro.
minosiro/lib/
# Basic components of file and structure info in minosiro, also with path generator utility.
minosiro/lib/file/
# Network ops for local gateway, domain host; Also some general ops like download; For apps, it now integrates with Twitter's API.
minosiro/lib/net/
# Model for exception, regex utility, yaml utility and the parser rule handler.
minosiro/lib/util/
# 2.3. Required configs for minosiro.
minosiro/conf/
# Config for ddns, include all of gateway, cloudflare and target.
minosiro/conf/ddns[.default].yaml 
# Config for minosiro, include proxy to overcome censorship and structure of local directories.
minosiro/conf/minosiro[.default].yaml
# Keys & secrets to get contents on Twitter.
minosiro/conf/twitter[.default].yaml